Node.Description: Go to Accounts payable > Purchase orders > All purchase orders.
Use the Quick Filter to find records. For example, filter on the Purchase order field with a value of '00000637'.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
On the Action Pane, click Options.
Click Product safety data sheet log.
In the Priority field, enter or select a value.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
